question: Show me psychologists and psychiatrists from Harmony Wellness Center.
sql_query1:
SELECT Employees.FullName
FROM Employees
WHERE (Employees.Mental_Health_Career = "Psychologist" OR Employees.Mental_Health_Career = "Psychiatrist") AND Employees.Clinic = "Harmony Wellness Center"
sql_query2:
SELECT Employees.FullName
FROM Employees
WHERE Employees.Mental_Health_Career = "Psychologist" OR Employees.Mental_Health_Career = "Psychiatrist" AND Employees.Clinic = "Harmony Wellness Center"
interpretation1: What psychologists are from Harmony Wellness Center and what psychiatrists are from the same clinic?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all psychologists and also provide a list of psychiatrists from Harmony Wellness Center.
